No. —.

Robins Dry Dock & Repair Company v. Marion L. Robinson, as Administratrix, etc. Submitted June 1, 1926. Decided June 7, 1926. Per Curiam.

Dismissed upon the authority of Stratton v. Stratton, 239 U. S. 55; Andrews v. Virginian Ry. Co., 248 U. S. 272; Matthews v. Huwe, 269 U. S. 262, 265-266; Southern Electric Co. v. Stoddard, Superintendent, 269 U. S. 186, 188-190.
